messages.title: RYAN SLAMS TORY LEAFLET
messages.content: Nasty and cowardly. Afraid to put their name to it. Last throw of dice for Bois. Enfield deserves better.

messages.title: Can you believe a word Joan Ryan says?
messages.content: The Tory leaflet they won't own up to.

mentions.candidate: Joan Ryan always tells the truth. Chase Farm is under threat.

images.caption: Joan Ryan always tells the truth. Chase Farm is under threat. Tories closed 3 Enfield Hospitals.

leaflet.additionalNotes: The leaflet is a reaction to a Tory leaflet that the candidate Joan Ryan criticizes for being dishonest and not owned up to by the creators.
